pips-solver/src/services/ensembleExtract.description: Multi-model ensemble extraction service that queries Gemini, Claude, and GPT-4o in parallel. Currently does NOT store per-model raw responses - this needs to be added for the comparison feature. Uses consensus voting to select best result.

pips-solver/src/app/components/AIVerific.description: Existing verification modal that shows extraction results before applying. This is where the 'Compare Models' button will be added to open the new ExtractionComparisonModal.
